<div>Hi,</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>I saw your page and saw that the Brocade VDX 6740 was not listed. I just
wanted to let you know that the VDX 6740 has dynamic buffer sharing of 
it&#8217;s low latency on-chip buffers and can be configured to allow any 
single port to borrow a maximum of 8000
 kilobytes using the commands:</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>
<div>qos rcv-queue limit 8000</div>
<div>qos tx-queue limit 8000</div>
</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Thank you,</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Jesse</div>
